{"tid":2384022,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"印度神童預言2月股災 係咪又中?","createTime":"2021-01-28T09:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T10:05:27.000Z","uid":108814,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"512ef87366bdbec261481aca117a7a76d991fe46","tid":2384022,"uid":108814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T09:48:19.000Z","msg":"第二波疾病爆發。但是，2月10日，會發生一場800年一次的六星聯珠，也就是地球、月球、土星、木星、水星、金星會連成一線。<br />\n<br />\n那麼，在這六星大合相的一天，很可能會發生什麼？<br />\n<br />\n小神童沒有提病毒大流行，他提的是經濟，注意，他提到的是經濟。他說，經濟可能全面崩潰。也就是說，六星連珠會導致經濟大崩盤。玄吧？上一次這種六星連珠的天象是800年前出現的，那個時候，全世界還是個僕僕實實的農業社會，以種糧食為主，大家自給自足，不存在什麼金融股票經濟崩盤的。但是現在可不一樣了，很多人手上都有股票呀，基金呀，什麼的。如果經濟崩潰，你手上的股票和基金安全嗎？帳面上的錢會打水漂嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe4e2ffdeaa02c4e71a66c1dec7484cbf273e90","tid":2384022,"uid":93998,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T09:50:33.000Z","msg":"2800 strong hold 50年<br />\n驚閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd72b9a39bd39ab2fefc9590771dc247947ac45","tid":2384022,"uid":108814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fe4e2ffdeaa02c4e71a66c1dec7484cbf273e90","tid":2384022,"uid":93998,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T09:50:33.000Z","msg":"2800 strong hold 50年<br />\n驚閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T09:52:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你係咪龔成"},{"pid":"53268f5b35d979406ff8caf0a126af0d47edc209","tid":2384022,"uid":173184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T09:52:55.000Z","msg":"Link?"},{"pid":"bacee6da8fb0d44928ce68845bcae9ca093